<li>Sending love and prayers your way. May her soul rest in eternal peace.</li>
<li>Thinking of you all and sending my deepest condolences.  Your mother was a wonderful woman.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, we offer our prayers and support.  May God comfort you.</li>
<li>Your mother's kindness and love will forever be cherished. We are so sorry for your loss.</li>
<li>May God welcome her into His loving embrace and grant you strength to cope.</li>
<li>We were blessed to know your mother.  Her spirit will live on through you.</li>
<li>In our thoughts and prayers.  May her soul find eternal rest.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love during this time of sorrow.  May God be with you.</li>
<li>May the memories of your mother bring you comfort during this difficult time.</li>
<li>We are so saddened by the loss of your mother. Our hearts go out to you.</li>
<li>Your mother was a remarkable woman, and she will be dearly missed.</li>
<li>May God's love surround you and give you comfort in your sorrow.</li>
<li>Praying for peace and solace for you and your family.</li>
    

